title: The 6 parameters to the -affine option
pid: 1993553a-68ab-47d7-a836-b1967893acf4
body: |2-
   are these:
     sx,rx,ry,sy,tx,ty

  What they mean:
                                          | sx  rx  0 |
        | x', y', 1 |  =  | x, y, 1 |  *  | ry  sy  0 |
                                          | tx  ty  1 |
